WEBVTT

1
00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.160
Study: Hi, Mark.

2
00:03:36.130 --> 00:03:38.639
Study: How have you been feeling today?!

3
00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:40.090
Mark: I did my laundry! I wasn't thinking about my pain I was absorbed in what I was doing.

4
00:03:40.090 --> 00:03:44.469
Study: How did you feel after that?

5
00:03:44.470 --> 00:03:45.040
Mark: I did feel the pain after I got done with my chores.

6
00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:48.210
Study: And how did you respond to that feeling?

7
00:03:48.210 --> 00:03:49.790
Mark: I was noticing it but I didn't get stuck on the feeling.

8
00:03:49.930 --> 00:03:51.489
Mark: Nice to be able to get away from that for a minute or two. 

9
00:03:51.490 --> 00:03:53.200
Study: Okay. And did you feel like you were able to change how you approach your experiences?

10
00:04:11.790 --> 00:04:13.020
Mark: I felt like I was able to do things I wouldn't normally be able to do. Like the sciatica didn't get in the way how it usually does.
